the general's profile online.

237
00:13:49,339 --> 00:13:52,258
When she's on-camera,
Monica only looks at Monica.

238
00:13:52,259 --> 00:13:55,605
- Parker, what's your 20?
- Seconds away.

239
00:14:01,751 --> 00:14:04,315
