243
00:14:13,031 --> 00:14:14,748
- Then we celebrate.
- Celebrate?

244
00:14:14,749 --> 00:14:17,690
Denial means guilt.
Refusal means more guilt.

245
00:14:17,812 --> 00:14:21,351
Punch out my cameraman,
and I'll kiss you on the mouth.

246
00:14:29,730 --> 00:14:30,847
I knew it.

247
00:14:31,232 --> 00:14:32,885
- We've got a shadow.
- What?

248
00:14:32,886 --> 00:14:37,739
It means you're being followed.
It means there's some meat on this bone.

249
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:45,112
All right, we're rolling.

250
00:14:45,957 --> 00:14:49,505
My friends, we are outside
the office of General Mark Chesler...

251
00:14:49,506 --> 00:14:53,125
to discover the truth about
America's secret prisons.

252
00:14:55,915 --> 00:14:59,477
