253
00:14:59,478 --> 00:15:03,178
General, who is being held
in the secret underground bunkers?

254
00:15:03,943 --> 00:15:05,342
I am late to a meeting.

255
00:15:05,343 --> 00:15:08,246
Then you don't deny
that these prisons exist?

256
00:15:08,368 --> 00:15:10,597
